The common thread that runs throughout the Cannabis Industry is a lack of capital and liquidity for the significant real estate, cultivation and production infrastructure needs of businesses, particularly those involved directly in the production and sale of cannabis and cannabis products. Mentioned facts present significant opportunities for the Project Canabio to achieve considerably high returns relative to the risks of secured investing in real estate and hard, underlying assets.   CANABIO TOKEN ▂▂▂▂▂▂▂▂▂  In order to achieve project goals, Canabio blockchain project will put in emission, in one stage $100M Canabio tokens, per initial price of $0.4.
